		screentext 2822 163 135 28672 0 0 409 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
		qputs 409 damage output. It also comes with a
		screentext 2822 163 141 28672 0 0 409 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
		qputs 409 red-dot sight for accuracy, and an
		screentext 2822 163 147 28672 0 0 409 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
		qputs 409 underslung grenade launcher for
		screentext 2822 163 153 28672 0 0 409 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
		qputs 409 those unsubtle moments.
		screentext 2822 163 159 28672 0 0 409 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
		}

